dct_title_s: Calbayog, Philippine Islands, Samar Province, Samar. A.M.S. S901
dct_description_sm: AMS 2. Alternate title: Calbayog. In upper left margin : Philippine city plans 1:5,000 (approx.). Polyconic projection.Projection ticks approximate. Relief shown by form lines.Complied from Calbayog 1:3,600, 1901; Calbayog, Samar, U.S. Navy, 1:2,400, 1939; US&GS Topographic Field Survey Sheet P985, 1:20,000, 1912; controlled mosaic 1:20,000, prior to 1940.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1944.
